{"tid":913074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社】養起民間研究，只差四十人","createTime":"2018-11-23T06:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T10:14:06.000Z","uid":138409,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"988c95a45592ce653a9d055a051dbac3598de9eb","tid":913074,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pC2tUKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpC2tUKF.jpg&h=e57768ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/2062692950493434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fposts%2F2062692950493434&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2BtqwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=2b0de4a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/posts/2062692950493434</a><br />\n日前公佈眾籌後，大家的熱烈回應實在令我們十分感動！初步整理眾籌成果，我們已收到72位月捐者由$100至$1000不等的捐款，<span style=\"color: red;\">約完成增加3萬元月捐額的60%，只需要多40位月捐$300的義士相助，本研社現時7位全職員工就可全部留低</span>，繼續同香港人並肩作戰喇！<br />\n<br />\n為回饋各位支持者，我們準備了一些小禮物，作為2018年度眾籌的回禮。包括一直很受歡迎的「香港地、小人多」tote bag、「田野考察」及「研究自主」tee也會重版出來！我們更聯同本地手工釀造啤酒廠 HK Brewcraft 生產「香港地、小人啤」，目前正密鑼緊鼓製作中，預計於明年一月完成，齊齊啤啤佢~ 🍻🍻<br />\n<br />\n此外，我們正籌備兩至三個「田野考察 tour」，主題包括東大嶼海域、新界棕地和郊野公園導賞等，由本研社成員或邀請神秘嘉賓帶團，同大家一齊將香港土地發展問題睇清睇楚！由於舉辦考察團成本較高，我們會優先給月捐$300以上或單額捐款$5000以上的朋友參加，報名詳情將不日公佈。<br />\n<br />\n心動不如行動！希望各位有意捐助的朋友盡早完成付款手續啦~ 也請幫忙推介給可能對本研社工作有興趣的朋友，讓籌款更快達標，各位研究員可早日將全副心力放回研究工作上。<br />\n<br />\n在揭破官商黑幕、追尋知識與真相的路上，我們需要你的支持。<br />\n<br />\n💰立即捐款：<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us%2F&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2BtqwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=109295c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us/</a><br />\n🌏了解更多：<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/about-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fabout-us%2F&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2BtqwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3b2f89d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/about-us/</a><br />\n<br />\nFor English version, please see:<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us-en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us-en%2F&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2BtqwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=69fa5f37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us-en/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/about-us-en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fabout-us-en%2F&d=9VGb%2F0e%2BiPoaNMotUy%2BtqwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=27b90437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/about-us-en/</a><br />\n<br />\n我們在極短時間內製作網頁和眾籌計劃，資料或有未完善處，請多多包涵。如有任何查詢，歡迎pm本專頁或電郵至info@liber-research.com，感謝！"},{"pid":"eb32a28c27a3e4cc4daf22c1621ebbcb4cb665f4","tid":913074,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jBJMHzf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjBJMHzf.png&h=92f461ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}